# Implementation Plan Conventions

- When drafting a task-backed implementation plan from this repo, write it to
  `../haderach-tasks/implementation-plans/`.
- Do not store task-backed implementation plans in `.cursor/` or
  `haderach-platform/docs/`.
- When a task exists, name the plan
  `<task-id>-<short-slug>-implementation-plan.md`.
- Update the related task file in `../haderach-tasks/tasks/` to link to the new
  plan path.
- The Cursor plan format is fine to keep; only the storage location changes.
